{"tid":1617606,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［注意］小心fb上嘅假本土新聞","createTime":"2019-10-04T00:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T20:58:18.000Z","uid":3177,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"605e888e4f00a147d7ef312e5d068962af9e9ad8","tid":1617606,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:28:23.000Z","msg":"轉貼：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/1463038647118476/posts/2478379578917706?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F1463038647118476%2Fposts%2F2478379578917706%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GZj7jGrzIfagxCK2eNaONkM%3D&h=f6b6609e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/1463038647118476/posts/2478379578917706?sfns=mo</a><br />\n嘅fb post<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【假本土新聞】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oTWzzRO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoTWzzRO.jpg&h=5fd8c7f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早排見到一個扮《本土新聞》嘅 content farm，真正嘅《本土新聞》網址係 <a href=\"http://localpresshk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flocalpresshk.com&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GZj7jGrzIfagxCK2eNaONkM%3D&h=746deaac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">localpresshk.com</a>，但個 content farm 就用 &quot;hklocalpress&quot;<br />\n<br />\n其實只要你一 click 入去，就會發現轉咗網址變成duckhk. com，一望就知係 content farm，另外仲有兩個網址係 news-lihkg 同 backup-lihkg，都係抄新聞、抄連登post。<br />\n<br />\n不過最近先發現有埋 Facebook page，叫「香港本土新聞 Hong Kong Press」，仲有成萬八人like。呢排我 newsfeed 上都見到多咗 content farm，要辨認其實一啲都唔難，通常都有幾個模式︰<br />\n<br />\n1. 網址奇怪（見過最離譜嘅係叫 on9news，而家都仲見到有人 share）；<br />\n2. 網址正常，但click入去就會即刻轉另一個唔相關嘅網址（縮短網址唔計）；<br />\n3. 內容嚟自其他媒體、論壇，直接抄（例如左下攞咗香港01張圖）；<br />\n4. 版面無美感（搵錢之嘛砌咁靚做乜，啲人都會睇㗎啦）。<br />\n<br />\n希望唔使再教大家咩係 content farm 同點解有害啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18963b2c97831471d53635c2428fbd0cf22ea9e0","tid":1617606,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:31:17.000Z","msg":"很重要 自推一下"},{"pid":"7d8847e49123732f29f88d6f965da1d8d824e1f1","tid":1617606,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:41:39.000Z","msg":"pilushhhhhhhhh"},{"pid":"c430f8d956b67b785b3ac8c5557c4e8b5c8d6f17","tid":1617606,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:48:43.000Z","msg":"pushhhhh"},{"pid":"e4ecc675ba72d4198f3ef34e6dae50d03598cff7","tid":1617606,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:49:29.000Z","msg":"REPORT LA"},{"pid":"ca9a7f40393230d876bcbb49547da29386dce5f7","tid":1617606,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:49:45.000Z","msg":"#請廣傳 <br />\n<br />\n香港人俾政府恰到上心口！<br />\n「反蒙面法」有機會今日立埋<br />\n如果你連三罷公投都唔表態<br />\n你 註定輸一世！<br />\n<br />\n公投截止日期：10月11日中午12點<br />\n<br />\nThe Government treat all HongKongers as nothing and they also want to pass the anti-mask law to tackle protesters.<br />\nIt is time for us to speak up! Let&rsquo;s give your opinion on performing general strike.<br />\n<br />\nDeadline: 11 Oct 2019 1200 HKT<br />\n<br />\n公投傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit